762
01:07:23,880 --> 01:07:27,620
<i>I'm so happy that I was
born as your daughter.</i>

763
01:07:27,620 --> 01:07:30,270
<i>Take our Hae Dang and
go someplace far away.</i>

764
01:07:30,270 --> 01:07:34,130
<i>I need to see you suffer
because of your child.</i>

765
01:07:34,140 --> 01:07:36,230
<i>I can't stand to see you. Get out.</i>

766
01:07:36,230 --> 01:07:38,630
<i>You are going to become
the wife of a murderer.</i>

767
01:07:38,630 --> 01:07:40,980
<i>Mother? Give me a break.</i>

768
01:07:40,980 --> 01:07:43,250
<i>What kind of person
was your child's father?</i>

769
01:07:43,250 --> 01:07:47,040
<i>Madam Yoo Ji Na told me she
doesn't know who the father is.</i>

770
01:07:47,040 --> 01:07:50,380
<i>Yes, Father it's Yoon Hee. Stepmother...</i>

771
01:07:50,380 --> 01:07:54,750
<i>Don't talk ill of her.
I'm worried that Yoon Hee is too sweet.</i>

772
01:07:54,750 --> 01:07:57,780
<i>I'm going to be a good big brother
to your sisters and do everything I can.</i>

773
01:07:57,780 --> 01:08:01,350
<i>Pay me back if we see
each other in the next life.</i>

774
01:08:01,350 --> 01:08:04,580
<i>I told you it's this week.
I'll send Kyung Soo to you.</i>
